<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <title>Main page</title>
    <script src="/js/home/index.js" defer></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include ('../layouts/header') %>

    <div class="container input-group mb-2 Likethings-containers">
      <div class="container Likethings-items">
        <h4>당신에게 맞는 숙소를 정해봅시다!</h4>
        <form
          action="/write_process"
          method="POST"
          class="list-group Likethings-items-list"
        >
          <select
            name="quest-people"
            class="list-group-item Likethings-items-quests"
          >
            <option value="none" selected>
              === 1. 같이 가는 사람은 몇 명인가요? ===
            </option>
            <option value="quest-people-one" name="people">1명</option>
            <option value="quest-people-two">2명</option>
            <option value="quest-people-three">3명</option>
            <option value="quest-people-more">4명 이상</option>
          </select>
          <select
            name="quest-child"
            class="list-group-item Likethings-items-quests"
          >
            <option value="none" selected>
              === 2. 미취학아동(만6~12세)이 동반하는 일정인가요? ===
            </option>
            <option value="quest-child-yes">네</option>
            <option value="quest-child-no">아니오</option>
          </select>
          <select
            name="quest-senior"
            class="list-group-item Likethings-items-quests"
          >
            <option value="none" selected>
              === 3. 어르신(만 65세이상)이 동반하는 일정인가요? ===
            </option>
            <option value="quest-senior-yes">네</option>
            <option value="quest-senior-no">아니오</option>
          </select>
          <select
            name="quest-bed"
            class="list-group-item Likethings-items-quests"
          >
            <option value="none" selected>
              === 4. 침대는 어떤 것을 선호하나요? ===
            </option>
            <option value="quest-bed-single">싱글</option>
            <option value="quest-bed-twin">트윈</option>
            <option value="quest-bed-double">더블</option>
          </select>
          <select
            name="quest-costLimit"
            class="list-group-item Likethings-items-quests"
          >
            <option value="none" selected>
              === 5. 1인당 숙소 비용의 최소 한도 금액은 얼마인가요? ===
            </option>
            <option value="quest-costLimit-down5">5만원 미만</option>
            <option value="quest-costLimit-down10">10만원 미만</option>
            <option value="quest-costLimit-top10">10만원 이상</option>
          </select>
          <select
            name="quest-priority"
            class="list-group-item Likethings-items-quests"
          >
            <option value="none" selected>
              === 6. 숙소에 머물 때 가장 우선 순위에 두는 것은 무엇인가요? ===
            </option>
            <option value="quest-priority-facility">근처 편의시설 여부</option>
            <option value="quest-priority-goodViews">좋은 경치와 전망</option>
            <option value="quest-priority-multiFacility">
              다중이용시설 여부
            </option>
            <option value="quest-priority-breakfast">조식여부 여부</option>
          </select>
          <button>submit</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
